{
  "stem": "24466.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- yes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got this enough, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went on one mission, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to [NON-ENGLISH], and I told him about the whole story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he sent a patrol to get us out from there to come back to the town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Vilna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And organizing and ask us, together with him, not far from Vilna, Valakampiai, to organize.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was already the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was, the Russians, the front was coming nearer the borders of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To organize partisans amongst the villages in the-- Valakampiai.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Valakampiai.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only the leader.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism was very high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will finish us off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could hear already, you know, the-- from the-- that-- high-- not the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- we heard already that the-- the front is coming closer, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could hear the-- the-- so we said to ourself, oh, the best idea would be not to sit because a lot of Germans already were still in Vilna, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're all-- all-- all-- what-- run away from the front and so on, and that was not far.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Valakampiai wasn't far from-- from Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we said to ourself, the best thing is to-- we will postpone, postpone arrangements of organizing the partisans there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that happens in a few days, three, four, five days, I believe, that the Russian Army took over Vilna.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where were you at that point?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Valkampiai.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian soldiers, well, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] There was a place they called [NON-ENGLISH] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Vilna, and the SS men there were barricading themselves to fight still the advanced Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through loudspeakers, they were calling, the police, give up, give up, give up, you're-- you're-- give up.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
